I"<p>Ingredients:</p>
<ul>
  <li>1⁄4 cup flax seed meal</li>
  <li>1⁄2 teaspoon baking powder</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon cinnamon</li>
  <li>1 egg</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon oil</li>
  <li>sugar to taste (or honey, stevia)</li>
</ul>

<p>Directions:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Mix all ingredients in a coffee mug.</li>
  <li>Micorowave for one minute on high.</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<p>This flax muffin is quick, vertsatile (just mix in other goodies), and only makes one at a time, so you’ve got no huge tray to tempt you. Custom muffins every morning!</p>
